Showing a macOS service in the menu

I have written a simple Automator workflow which process selected text. It does the job, and is available from most applications in the Service menu in the Text group.

I have one application, the application I really wanted to use it for, which doesn’t show the text group in the Services menu, but it does show the development and general group.

Is there a technique to either show the Text group or to change the grouping of the workflow to the Development or General group?
